<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4594340>
    dc:description "Fig. 4. Cladogram representation of the classification of Psyllidae Latreille, 1807 adopted here, node symbols indicate subfamilies with poor to moderate support (white), or strong support (black) in molecular analyses (Percy et al. 2018). For Katacephalinae subfam. nov. no node symbol is given as only a single species was included in the analyses." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4594340/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

